posting_body: ['Central heating and air conditioning - Dedicated laundry room with full sized washer and dryer including storage - Beautiful eat-in kitchen with carefully selected materials of Slate, Granite, Oak, and Stainless Steel - Gas cooking- 6.9KW Solar System: low electric bill.- Level 2 EV car charging station-', 'Whole house soft water system - Pets OK with additional deposit - Deposit equal to one months rent - Trash service included - Fantastic Walk Score of 86!', '- Walking distance to everything in Downtown San Jose and minutes to the San Jose Airport Application.', 'Large inside laundry room.', 'Powder room.', 'Large master suite with huge walk in closet.', 'Master bathroom has a tub with shower.', 'New paint inside and out.', 'New carpeting on the stairs and all bedrooms.', 'Newer carpet in living and family rooms.', 'Air conditioning.', 'Two car attached garage with lots of storage.', 'Security System.', 'Washer and Dryer included.', 'Private back yard.', 'Great neighbors either side of this home.updated bathrooms, wood burning fireplace plus a sparkling pool in the backyard.', 'No refrigerator included.', 'Washer/Dryer hookups.', 'Garbage included.', 'Tenant responsible for all other utilities/services.2 car garage.', 'No pets, no smoking.', 'Kitchen is gourmet chef with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, 6 burner Wolf gas stove, Bosch dishwasher, two huge ovens and a built-in microwave.', 'Separate pantry with industrial shelving.', 'Cabinetry is custom cherry and office & kitchen beautifully refinished maple floors.', 'Deep green granite counters and slate backsplash.', 'Under cabinet lighting.', '1st floor bath & mudroom have matching hand cut slate tile with leaf detailing.', 'Mud room off the kitchen with extra storage exits to a beautifully redone backyard.', 'CONTACT   US   NOW   40 8 4 18 1 75 8']
